    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey&#8212;U S America<ptr target="tex.00482_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1891-06-05">June 5 '91</date>
                </dateline> 
            </opener>
            <p>Thanks, dear friend&#8212;&#38; thanks, friends Bessie &#38; Isabella Ford,<ptr
                target="med.00873_n1"/> R D Roberts of Cambridge,<ptr target="tex.00482_n4"/> &#38;
                William,<ptr target="n3025"/> Arthur<ptr target="n5001"/> &#38; Ethel Thompson,<ptr target="tex.00482_n3"/> for the welcome &#38;
                noble birthday gift wh' has safely reach'd me (40 pounds) &#38; is hereby
                    receipted.<ptr target="tex.00482_n2"/></p>
            <p>I still hold the fort, (after a fashion)&#8212;send you my latest &#38; doubtless
                concluding chirps of L of G. by this mail&#8212;also sent you lame report of late
                birth-day spree<ptr target="loc.04326_n3"/>&#8212;I sit up most of the time&#8212;but am a fearful wreck f'm
                grippe, gastric &#38; bladder malady &#38;c &#38;c&#8212;my vocalization &#38; right
                arm power &#38; (sort o') ratiocination left middling fair&#8212;Dr Bucke<ptr
                    target="n0119"/> has been here&#8212;has gone home to Canada&#8212;H
                    Stafford<ptr target="n0590"/> is living down as farmer (address Ashland, Camden
                County, New Jersey) is well&#8212;has been quite ill&#8212;has two
                children<ptr target="loc.03961_n5b"/>&#8212;Herbert Gilchrist<ptr target="n0262"/> at Centreport, Suffolk Co: N
                Y: well&#8212;am sitting here comfortable as I write&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
